---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Adult Candle Making Night"
  description="Adult-focused candle making experience perfect for date nights and group events in Centerville, TN."
  price="$25-35 per person"
  duration="2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="adult candle making, date night activity, group events, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Adult Candle Making Night - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>
      Escape the ordinary with our Adult Candle Making Night. Perfect for date nights, girls' nights out, corporate team bonding, or just a fun evening with friends. Create beautiful candles while enjoying a relaxed, adult-focused atmosphere.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      This is candle making designed for adults who want to have fun, get creative, and enjoy good company. You'll pour beautiful candles while our instructors guide you through the process in a relaxed, social environment. Perfect for everyone from complete beginners to experienced crafters.
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Relaxed, adult-focused atmosphere</li>
      <li>Premium soy wax and fragrances</li>
      <li>Wide selection of fragrance options</li>
      <li>Beautiful container choices</li>
      <li>Expert hands-on instruction</li>
      <li>Refreshments available</li>
      <li>Take home 2-3 beautiful candles</li>
      <li>Social, fun experience</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Date Nights:</strong> Romantic creative couples activity</li>
      <li><strong>Girls' Nights:</strong> Fun friend bonding time</li>
      <li><strong>Corporate Events:</strong> Team building and networking</li>
      <li><strong>Adult Groups:</strong> Clubs, meetups, celebrations</li>
      <li><strong>Bachelor/Bachelorette:</strong> Pre-wedding fun</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Group & Event Options</h3>
    <p>
      We specialize in hosting adult groups! Whether it's 2 people or 20, we create a fun, memorable experience. Our café has refreshments, and our open space works perfectly for group events.
    </p>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and introduction (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Select your fragrance and container (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Hands-on candle pouring with instruction (60-75 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches and chat time (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take home your beautiful creations!</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $25-35 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> Flexible (2-20+ people)<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <h3>Group Event Pricing</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>2-4 people:</strong> $25-35 per person<br />
      <strong>5-10 people:</strong> $22-30 per person (group rate)<br />
      <strong>10+ people:</strong> Custom pricing available<br />
      <strong>Private events:</strong> Available upon request
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Plan your adult night!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com for group bookings and event details. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Best date night we've had in years! Making candles together was so fun and romantic. We'll definitely be back!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Chris & Melissa</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Our team building event was a huge success! Everyone made beautiful candles and had a blast. Highly recommend!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Rebecca T., Corporate Event</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Girls' night out couldn't have been better! We made candles, hung out, and left with beautiful creations. Already planning our next visit!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>The Garden Club Group</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Pour Your Own Candle Class</h3>
        <p>Create beautiful hand-poured candles with custom colors and scents.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/pour-your-own-candle-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Candle Making Workshop</h3>
        <p>Learn professional candle-making techniques from start to finish.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/candle-making-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Custom Scent Candle Creation</h3>
        <p>Design your own unique fragrance blend for a personalized candle.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/custom-scent-candle-creation" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
